  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I remember we had dynamic min and max set on the inputs at some point, but it was removed due to usability concerns. I don't remember the full history though, so we'd need to look at it again to see what the right solution would be.\r\n\r\nFor the time being, you can of course use useRange already and render the min and max yourself if you use your own inputs.\r\n\r\nOne thing to keep in mind as well is that changing the dom in most cases is a breaking change, so we can't just add a min/max dom property without this having impact for people eg already transforming or swapping the values already",
    "created_at": "2023-09-12T07:29:56Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/5842#issuecomment-1715154623",
