  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "As \"disabled\" on a submit button is also not always considered a best practice ([source](https://medium.com/@izzmo/anti-pattern-using-disabled-or-read-only-for-form-input-e2c24c669f5b)) I wonder if a custom rendering isn't the best way for you to go?",
